data.name: genereg
data.description: Python library for the analysis of gene expression regulation systems of genes of interest in TCGA cancers.

evidence: "This library implements a method for analyzing the regulation systems of target genes in a specific genetic pathology" (described as a library, indicating it is used as a dependency).

"Adopting a linear regression approach, it builds a predictive model for the regulation of target genes expression, in order to identify the relevant features that explain the regulation of each gene of interest" (directly performs domain-specific analysis for research results).
PyPI badge and link: "[![PyPI version]...](https://pypi.org/project/genereg/)" (indicates distribution via the PyPI package registry).
